81033895;TV Show;Hardy Bucks;;Martin Maloney, Owen Colgan, Chris Tordoff, Peter Cassidy, Tom Kilgallon, Michael Salmon, Wayne Lynch, Tommy Miller;Ireland; January 11, 2019;2018;TV-MA;4 Seasons;TV Comedies;A circle of young men entertain vague ambitions involving quick cash, women and showbiz in this mockumentary on small-town Irish life in County Mayo.